/target

# Local agent task-tracking workspace — never committed.
/.work/

# Per-user scratch notes — never committed. Use these names freely for
# throwaway planning/working files.
*.local.md
task_plan.md
findings.md
progress.md

# Rust
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# `processkit` `RecordReplayRunner::save` advisory lock sidecar — created next
# to a cassette while (re)recording, released and left as a harmless empty
# file on drop. Never part of the committed fixture (crates/*/tests/cassettes/).
*.json.lock

# Nix
/result
